# Output format

Return a JSON object matching this exact schema:

{
  "title": "<the Objective>",
  "description": "<optional context, may be null>",
  "key_results": [
    {
      "description": "<the KR>",
      "metric_type": "<one of: number, percentage, currency, boolean, milestone>",
      "baseline_value": <number — the current value or 0 for milestones>,
      "target_value": <number — what we are aiming for>,
      "current_value": <number — same as baseline for new drafts>,
      "unit": "<optional: 'users', 'USD', '%', 'NPS' — null if metric is percentage or boolean or milestone>",
      "weight": <number — 1.0 unless this KR matters more than the others>
    }
  ]
}

Output ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no commentary, no markdown fences.
